        {
            "title": "美國假日周首次申領失業救濟人數小幅降至20.9萬人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"US Labor Department\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"705\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r722wKgnbp9itWEWeeKEPA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9aaf8830ac4bf2ee73567fae90d2aea6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">US Labor Department</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國上周的申領失業救濟人數變動不大，進一步顯示勞動力市場有所企穩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國勞工部周四公佈的數據顯示，截至1月24日當周，首次申領失業救濟人數小幅下降1,000人，至20.9萬人；此前一周的數據被上修。彭博調查的經濟學家預測中值為20.5萬人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當周涵蓋馬丁·路德·金紀念日，同時美國多地遭遇嚴重冬季風暴。假期和惡劣天氣期間部分人短期內無法工作，因此數據往往會出現波動。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"705\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Fb9eqpiganzfBYLLaKmRXQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9e316cedc82cb5a16d59d09c1cdf07ca\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑒於很多人仍在遭遇斷電，企業運營中斷可能會持續更久，可能會促使更多人申請失業救濟。整體來看，勞動力市場近期出現了一些企穩跡象，促使聯儲會本周維持利率不變。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7cc88ea8-5c05-36fd-9220-f5cafc190dd2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至1月17日當周，持續申領失業救濟人數降至183萬人，為2024年9月以來最低。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首次申領失業救濟人數的四周移動平均值上周小幅升至206,250人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Jobless Claims Tick Down to 209,000 During Holiday Week (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%87%E6%97%A5%E5%91%A8%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%98%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%91%E6%BF%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B320-9%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA-140943343.html",
