        {
            "title": "瑞典央行維持利率不變 重申將在未來一段時間按兵不動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Riksbank\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"581\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FLK711mZvinANElGkBS8Lg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/829bcef0d86eac5b4c99e71d6a574f6b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Riksbank</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 瑞典央行連續第四個月按兵不動，並維持在明年之前不會調整利率的預測。越來越多的證據顯示經濟復甦將足夠強勁，能使通膨率保持在目標水平附近。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行周四宣布將基準利率維持在三年低位1.75%，符合接受彭博調查的所有17位經濟學家的預期。 由於沒有新的經濟預測，決策者重申了借貸成本應該會保持不變到年底後的觀點。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"581\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Eo9l7XgVZjELtz4B2L.mJQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/30e08241742733fbe5f64ee70a30d791\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「目前的政策利率水平應當有助於增強經濟活動，並使通膨在長期內穩定在目標水平附近，」該行官員表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a7ec182d-e2ab-3d05-af9a-75e37ed21b9f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，決策者們也提到不確定性正在增加，尤其是來自美國的不確定性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他們稱「2026年初的地緣政治局勢劇變，這在很大程度上源於美國政府的外交政策舉措」，並警告「情況可能迅速變化」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「儘管出現一些波動，但金融市場的整體反應有限，不過美元持續走弱，包括對瑞典克朗，」他們表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Sweden Holds Rate and Repeats Pause Plan as Upturn Builds</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Joel Rinneby、Charles Daly、Christopher Jungstedt、Alastair Reed.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
